summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5061 for the improvement of 44th Avenue Southwest, from West Cambridge Street on the east to Brace Point Drive by constructing wood curbs and gutters and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 58169 as amended by Ordinance No. 58553, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
